org.deeplearning4j.ui.storage.sqlite

Class J7FileStatsStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.ui.storage.sqlite.J7FileStatsStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.StatsStorage, org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.StatsStorageRouter

    public class J7FileStatsStorage
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.StatsStorage
    A Java 7 compatible file-based StatsStorage implementation, based on SQLite. Note: Where possible, use FileStatsStorage which should be faster (is based on MapDB). Obviously, the storage formats for J7FileStatsStorage and FileStatsStorage are incompatible.
